    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Light red blend</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">A useful entry-point bottle when you want freshness and low-intervention energy without jumping straight into unstable or overly funky wine.</p>
  </div>
